item.title: Limited Room Seen for BTP-Bund Spread to Tighten After Moody's Improved Italy's Outlook
item.description: Moody’s Investors Service’s upgrade of the outlook on Italy’s Baa3 rating to stable from negative favors some further short-term tightening dynamics for Italian government bonds, Morgan Stanley Research said.

item.title: Sam Altman Not Returning as CEO of OpenAI
item.description: Sam Altman’s bid to return to OpenAI faltered, as the board that fired him opted not to agree to proposed terms of his reinstatement. Emmett Shear, former CEO of Twitch, was named interim CEO.

item.title: Nikkei Falls 0.6% on Likely Profit-Taking, JPY Strength

item.title: NASA Has an Infrastructure Problem. Here's Why It Matters.
item.description: The Deep Space Network, NASA’s main communications infrastructure, is overburdened. That’s raising concerns about the network’s ability to support future missions, as NASA pivots toward extended human exploration of the moon.
